# Go Clean Architecture Template — Project Overview

## Tech Stack

| Category | Technology |
| :--- | :--- |
| Language | Go 1.21+ |
| Web Framework | Gin |
| Database | PostgreSQL (GORM) |
| Dependency Injection | Google Wire |
| API Docs | Swagger/OpenAPI |
| Logging | slog (JSON format) |
| Password Hashing | bcrypt |
| Authentication | JWT |

## Architecture Principles

Uses **DDD + Clean Architecture** design. Core rule: **dependencies only point inward**.

```
External World (HTTP, DB, External APIs)
         ↓
Adapter Layer (Delivery, Repository, Gateway)
         ↓
UseCase Layer (Business logic orchestration, interface definitions)
         ↓
Domain Layer (Core entities, business rules)
```

## Domain Modules

| Domain | Directory | Responsibility |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| User | `internal/user/` | User registration, login, authentication |

> When adding new domain modules, follow the same pattern under `internal/{domain}/`.

## Directory Structure

Each domain module follows a unified structure:

```
{domain}/
├── domain/           # Domain layer: core entities and business rules
│   └── {domain}.go
├── usecase/          # UseCase layer: business logic orchestration
│   ├── {domain}.go   # {Domain}Manager implementation
│   ├── interfaces.go # Port interface definitions (Repository/Gateway)
│   ├── dto/          # UseCase-level DTOs
│   └── mock/         # mockgen-generated mocks
└── adapter/          # Adapter layer: external interface implementations
    ├── delivery/http/
    │   ├── handler/  # HTTP handlers
    │   ├── router/   # Route registration
    │   └── dto/      # HTTP-level DTOs
    └── repository/   # Data persistence
```

## Shared Components

| Module | Directory | Responsibility |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Server | `internal/shared/adapter/delivery/` | HTTP server assembly and startup |
| Router | `internal/shared/adapter/delivery/http/router/` | Central route registration |
| Middleware | `internal/shared/adapter/delivery/http/middleware/` | ErrorHandler and other middleware |
| DI | `internal/di/` | Wire dependency injection config |

## Shared Libraries

| Module | Directory | Responsibility |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| config | `pkg/config/` | Configuration loading (Viper) |
| db | `pkg/db/` | Database connection (GORM + Postgres) |
| auth | `pkg/auth/` | JWT token service |
| crypto | `pkg/crypto/` | Password hashing |
| log | `pkg/log/` | Structured logging (slog) |
| utils | `pkg/utils/` | AppError unified error handling |

## Feature Development Order

Domain → UseCase → Repository/Gateway → Handler → Router → Swagger → Tests → Wire DI

## Common Commands

```bash
make build   # Build
make serve   # Start server
make di      # Generate dependency injection code
make doc     # Generate Swagger docs
make lint    # Run linter
make test    # Run tests
make fmt     # Format code
make mock    # Generate mocks
```
